# Ignore raw generation data
Minority/

# Images (binary, large)
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.webp

# Model files
*.pt
*.pth
*.ckpt
*.safetensors

# Editor
*.swp
*~

**/*.json

# Keep safety evaluation outputs trackable.
!Safety/
!Safety/Minority/
